Paper: hep-th/9709120

Date: 1997-09-16

Title: Gauge Transformations For Self/Anti-Self Charge Conjugate States

Comments: ReVTeX file, 7pp., accepted in "Acta Physica Polonica B"

Journal-ref: Acta Phys.Polon. B29 (1998) 619-627

Gauge transformations of type-II spinors are considered in theMajorana-Ahluwalia construct for self/anti-self charge conjugate states. Somespeculations on the relations of this model with the earlier ones are given.